### Add Item to Cart - Done 
POST {{CartService_HostAddress}}/addToCart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": 4,
    "stock": 7
}

### Update Item Quantity - Done
PUT {{CartService_HostAddress}}/updateStock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": 4,
    "stock": 16
}

### Delete Item from Cart - Done
DELETE {{CartService_HostAddress}}/deleteItem/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Clear Entire Cart - Done
POST {{CartService_HostAddress}}/clearCart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
